OL,6,FReport by ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,8,FProducer Lottie Kilraine
OL,10,FAfter decades of suffering alone, more
OL,11,Fwomen exposed to the controversial
OL,12,Fdrug Stilbestrol are breaking their
OL,13,Fsilence to speak out on what's been
OL,14,Fdescribed as one of the worst medical
OL,15,Fdisasters in NHS history.
OL,17,FITV News has brought together two
OL,18,Fmothers who were prescribed the anti-
OL,19,Fmiscarriage drug commonly known as DES
OL,20,Fin the 1960s.
