OL,6,FJenny Brooks, 88, who lives in
OL,7,FBerkshire, and 94-year-old Hilary
OL,8,FTasker, from Oxfordshire, have lived
OL,9,Fwith the guilt of taking the DES all
OL,10,Ftheir life.
OL,12,FIt was prescribed by NHS doctors, but
OL,13,Fthey fear it may have affected the
OL,14,Fhealth of their children.
OL,16,FBoth women described meeting another
OL,17,FDES mother as "a release" and said it
OL,18,Fhas made "a huge difference to finally
OL,19,Fbe able to talk about it".
