OL,6,FDES was a synthetic hormone prescribed
OL,7,Fto an estimated 300,000 women on the
OL,8,FNHS between the late 1930s and 1980s
OL,9,Fto treat several issues, including
OL,10,Fmiscarriage, until it was linked to
OL,11,Frare cancers and infertility in the
OL,12,Fdaughters of those who took it.
OL,14,FThe government has apologised to
OL,15,Fvictims of the DES drug scandal after
OL,16,Four year-long ITV News investigation
OL,17,Fexposed the scale of the harm caused,
OL,18,Fand the Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,19,Fhas agreed to meet victims in the new
OL,20,Fyear.
