OL,6,F'The pain was excruciating': Jenny's
OL,7,Fstory
OL,9,FThe decades may have passed, but Jenny
OL,10,FBrooks can still recall the hospital
OL,11,Fward in London where she was
OL,12,Fprescribed DES in 1960.
OL,14,FShe was in her early 20s and suffering
OL,15,Ffrom pregnancy complications.
OL,17,F"Looking back, I knew there was
OL,18,Fsomething not right, something that we
OL,19,Fweren't being told," Jenny told ITV
OL,20,FNews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
