OL,6,F"I was in the hospital with about five
OL,7,Fother ladies all in a row, all given
OL,8,Fthe same tablet for the same reason.
OL,9,FWe had to stay in bed the whole time
OL,10,Faway from our families, that was
OL,11,Freally quite traumatic."
OL,13,FShe believes she may have been part of
OL,14,Fa medical trial.
OL,16,FYears later in the 1990s she developed
OL,17,Fa rare type of gynaecological cancer
OL,18,Fwhich Jenny believes may be linked to
OL,19,Fher DES exposure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
