OL,6,FSeven operations, plastic surgery and
OL,7,Freconstruction followed. Treatment
OL,8,Fwhich has left her incontinent.
OL,10,F"It's had a massive impact on my
OL,11,Fhealth," she said. "The pain from one
OL,12,Foperation was excruciating, it came
OL,13,Flike a lightning flash."
OL,15,FIn November, Jenny, who is a retired
OL,16,Fmedical secretary, was among a group
OL,17,Fof campaigners who travelled to
OL,18,FWestminster to launch their campaign
OL,19,Ffor justice and raise awareness of DES
OL,20,Fand its toxic legacy.
