OL,6,F"We need to educate medical staff at
OL,7,Fall levels about this, not just
OL,8,Fgynaecologists, so it's out in the
OL,9,Fpublic, like Thalidomide and the
OL,10,Fdamage that did, but this (damage) is
OL,11,Fhidden," she added.
OL,13,F'You didn't question it': Hilary's
OL,14,Fstory
OL,16,FHilary Tasker, 94, from Thame was
OL,17,Fprescribed DES in 1960 while living in
OL,18,FCheshire.
