OL,6,F"I'd had about five miscarriages
OL,7,Fbefore I fell pregnant with my
OL,8,Fdaughter," she told ITV News.
OL,10,F"The doctors then put me to bed for a
OL,11,Fwhole seven months."
OL,13,FOn being prescribed DES, Hilary
OL,14,Frecalled how "times were different" in
OL,15,Fthe 1960s and you were not encouraged
OL,16,Fto question medical professionals and
OL,17,Fdoctors.
OL,19,F"If he decided he was going to give
OL,20,Fyou something, you didn't question
OL,21,Fit," she said.
