OL,6,FIn total, Hilary suffered nine
OL,7,Fmiscarriages.
OL,9,FMedical research suggests pregnant
OL,10,Fwomen who took DES may have a 30%
OL,11,Fhigher risk of breast cancer.
OL,13,FTheir daughters are 40 times more
OL,14,Flikely to develop clear cell
OL,15,Fadenocarcinoma of the vagina and
OL,16,Fcervix, a rare and aggressive form of
OL,17,Fcancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
