OL,6,FIt was only when her daughter, Helen
OL,7,FWestropp, began experiencing
OL,8,Fgynaecological problems in her teens
OL,9,Fand then developed breast cancer as an
OL,10,Fadult, that Hilary discussed the
OL,11,Fpotential impact of DES exposure with
OL,12,Fher family.
OL,14,FShe was shocked to learn how widely
OL,15,Fthe drug was used across the NHS, once
OL,16,Fseen as a panacea for pregnancy
OL,17,Fcomplications.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
