OL,6,F"At the time you had no knowledge of
OL,7,Fhow many other people were given it,"
OL,8,Fshe said. "It's only comparatively
OL,9,Frecently that's we've known the
OL,10,Fnumbers."
OL,12,FLike many women who took DES, Hilary
OL,13,Fsaid accessing her medical records to
OL,14,Funderstand the dosage of DES that she
OL,15,Fwas given had proved difficult.
OL,17,FThe casual way the drug was given out,
OL,18,Fpoor record keeping and the time that
OL,19,Fhas passed means that many women will
OL,20,Fnever find out the truth.
