OL,6,F'For some of us it's too late':
OL,7,FHelen's story
OL,9,FDES harm can be passed down the
OL,10,Fgenerations affecting the children of
OL,11,Fthose who took the drug, according to
OL,12,Fscientific studies.
OL,14,FHilary's daughter Helen, 64, believes
OL,15,FDES has had a huge effect on her
OL,16,Fhealth.
OL,18,F"I have a womb which is misformed,
OL,19,Fit's back to front," she told ITV
OL,20,FNews. "I never fell pregnant, and I
OL,21,Fhave a very bad immune system."
