OL,6,FShe later developed breast cancer and
OL,7,Fhas urged the government to improve
OL,8,Fmedical care and screening for the
OL,9,Fnext generation as soon as possible.
OL,11,F"For anybody who knows that they've
OL,12,Fbeen affected by it, there should be a
OL,13,Fproper screening programme put in,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"I'm particularly concerned about the
OL,17,Fnext generation down, because I think
OL,18,Fto some extent for some of us it's too
OL,19,Flate."
