OL,6,FHelen also believes it vital that the
OL,7,Fgovernment attempts to trace and
OL,8,Finform families that have been DES
OL,9,Fexposed and improve understanding of
OL,10,Fthe impacts of DES amongst the medical
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FShe says most doctors she has raised
OL,14,Fthe issue with "look at you with a
OL,15,Fblank face, they've never heard of it".
OL,17,FThe brand strategist and consultant
OL,18,Fwho lives in Oxfordshire is part of
OL,19,Fthe recently formed DES Justice UK
OL,20,Fgroup, made up of more than 400 people
OL,21,Faffected by DES.
