OL,6,FVictims and their families are calling
OL,7,Ffor a full statutory public inquiry.
OL,8,FThey also want medical research into
OL,9,Fthe long-term, intergenerational
OL,10,Feffects of the drug and a compensation
OL,11,Ffund.
OL,13,FIn November, the Health Secretary
OL,14,Fadmitted "the state got this wrong"
OL,15,Fafter our year-long ITV News
OL,16,Finvestigation revealing the scale of
OL,17,Fthe DES scandal and agreed to meet
OL,18,Fthose affected.
